FBIS4-53777 "dreas099_n_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 Vietnam Agreement Reached With U.S. on Liaison Offices Agreement Reached With U.S. on Liaison Offices BK2305032394 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 21 May 94 BK2305032394 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam English BFN [Text] U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher has held talks with Vietnamese Deputy Prime Minister Tran Duc Luong during the latter's visit to the United States. Mr. Christopher described the talks as constructive. A State Department spokesman said: Both sides have reached a compromise on the establishment of liaison offices between the two countries.
